       <h3>Plan B (non-thesis)</h3> 
       <p>The coursework requirements are the same as the M.S. Plan A requirements except that Thesis Research (CHE, PETE 5960) is not required. Plan B students take an additional 4 hours of elective course credits (total of 30 hours required).</p> 
       <p>M.S. Plan B students must write a paper on a topic assigned by the adviser. This paper must be submitted to the student's graduate committee for approval.</p> 
       <h3><b><b><b>Doctoral Program</b></b></b></h3> 
       <table border="1" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="2" frame="border" style="background-color: #d9d6d3; width: 350px;"> 
